00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:09,200
Don't forget that you have a boyfriend.

284
00:16:09,830 --> 00:16:11,090
Who was the one who went out

285
00:16:11,090 --> 00:16:12,760
to eat with that girl before?

286
00:16:12,950 --> 00:16:15,310
We're even now.

287
00:16:15,340 --> 00:16:16,540
It can work like that?

288
00:16:19,930 --> 00:16:20,990
Idiot.

289
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:22,240
That was my brother.

290
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:23,890
He is your brother?

291
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,590
Then, let's ask him to come back...

292
00:16:25,590 --> 00:16:27,390
He had something to take care of.

293
00:16:27,470 --> 00:16:28,000
Let's go.

294
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,120
Let's go home.

295
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,090
Let's go.

296
00:16:31,090 --> 00:16:33,750
Well... does your brother know we're together?

297
00:16:33,810 --> 00:16:35,610
I didn't get a chance to tell him.

298
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:39,440
When can I meet your grandpa and your brother?

299
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:41,010
You will.

300
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:41,800
Don't worry.

301
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,670
You need to introduce us to each other.

302
00:16:43,670 --> 00:16:44,370
Okay.

303
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,450
You want surveillance gear,

304
00:17:03,450 --> 00:17:05,410
but you wouldn't apply through the department

305
00:17:05,410 --> 00:17:07,630
because you are afraid of being bugged yourself?

306
00:17:07,630 --> 00:17:09,480
Zhouguo, do you know

307
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:11,550
why No Sir assigned me this mission?

308
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:13,800
He has his reasons. Not our place to ask.

309
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,119
Why can you all

310
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,329
trust the organization's orders

311
00:17:16,329 --> 00:17:17,950
so unconditionally?

312
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:21,060
Just doing whatever they instruct you to do.

313
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:25,560
Perhaps it's the subservience that's been passed down

314
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:28,420
through our Bai family line, etched into our bones.

315
00:17:28,890 --> 00:17:31,270
I know you can't accept it from the bottom of your heart,

316
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:31,840
but...

317
00:17:33,050 --> 00:17:34,870
do you dare to defy Grandpa?

318
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:05,120
What's wrong?

319
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,550
I have a cold.

320
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:08,810
I wanna some medicine.

321
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,800
Why are you up drinking alone

322
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:28,260
in the middle of the night?

323
00:18:30,260 --> 00:18:33,060
I was scolded by my thesis advisor this afternoon.

324
00:18:33,530 --> 00:18:35,990
So I'm drinking some beer to relieve stress.

325
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,440
Are you hiding something from me?

326
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,210
What do you mean?

327
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:50,090
Whether it's me almost being caught in a lie by Grandma

328
00:18:50,090 --> 00:18:52,090
or me encountering difficulties on a task,

329
00:18:52,090 --> 00:18:53,820
you're always there to help me.

330
00:18:55,990 --> 00:18:58,320
You're involved in everything in my life.

331
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:01,210
But when it comes to your matters, you won't let me get involved.

332
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:02,610
Aren't I your boyfriend?

333
00:19:06,450 --> 00:19:09,400
Getting scolded by my advisor happens all the time.

334
00:19:09,630 --> 00:19:11,360
It's really just a minor thing.

335
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,920
Then why don't you rely on me more?

336
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:17,050
Or do you think I'm not someone you can trust?

337
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:20,650
Of course not.

338
00:19:21,630 --> 00:19:23,540
I just don't want

339
00:19:23,730 --> 00:19:25,530
to trouble you with my problems.

340
00:19:32,530 --> 00:19:35,060
I know you're holding something back from me.

341
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,410
Bai,

342
00:19:40,570 --> 00:19:42,770
what do your family members do for work?

343
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:46,590
They're civil servants.

344
00:19:47,780 --> 00:19:50,160
Then, has Hei met them yet?

345
00:19:52,490 --> 00:19:53,360
Not yet.

346
00:19:56,910 --> 00:20:00,110
Maybe I still have a long way to go before I earn your trust.

347
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:02,230
But give me a little more time.

348
00:20:02,230 --> 00:20:04,070
I'll definitely become a better person

349
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:06,000
so you can feel more at ease with me.

350
00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:09,000
You're already great.

351
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:11,390
You love your family.

352
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:13,130
You're loyal to your friends.

353
00:20:15,410 --> 00:20:17,270
I'm the one who's not good enough.

354
00:20:20,450 --> 00:20:21,590
Bai.

355
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:24,800
Tell me what you're actually thinking.

356
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:28,830
If...

357
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:33,610
you get to know the real me someday,

358
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,220
you might regret it.

359
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:39,570
How could I?

360
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:43,910
You really trust me that much?

361
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,070
Of course.

362
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,360
How much do you trust me?

363
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:49,960
Other than my family,

364
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:52,360
you're the first person I've ever trusted.

365
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:54,980
Whenever I encounter a problem,

366
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:56,860
you're always the first one there to help me.

367
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:57,850
When I'm in danger,

368
00:20:57,850 --> 00:20:59,180
you stand in front of me.

369
00:20:59,560 --> 00:21:02,100
No matter what worries or past you have,

370
00:21:02,210 --> 00:21:03,800
I'll accept them all.

371
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,460
Bai.

372
00:21:09,330 --> 00:21:10,570
You must believe me.

373
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:17,510
Wait for me a second.

374
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,970
I need to use the bathroom.

375
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:24,590
I'm not that smart.

376
00:21:24,970 --> 00:21:27,890
I can't guess if you don't tell me.

377
00:21:29,770 --> 00:21:31,720
It shouldn't be just you giving me everything

378
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:33,290
while I give nothing back.

379
00:21:36,210 --> 00:21:37,640
Or do you think...

380
00:21:38,580 --> 00:21:39,840
I have nothing to give?

381
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:56,410
Bai,

382
00:21:56,410 --> 00:21:56,880
(Preview)
Bai,

383
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,080
did you put this
(Preview)

384
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,370
on my ear for me?
(Preview)

385
00:21:59,650 --> 00:22:00,850
It looks great on you.

386
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:03,320
If you've done something wrong for my sake,

387
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:04,890
I'd rather not have the surgery.

388
00:22:04,890 --> 00:22:05,830
Hei Jiali.

389
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:08,850
What kind of task pays enough to cover an entire surgery bill?

390
00:22:08,850 --> 00:22:10,570
You'd have to risk your life for that, right?

391
00:22:10,570 --> 00:22:11,950
I need more tasks.

392
00:22:12,450 --> 00:22:14,180
Why don't you let me help you?

393
00:22:14,230 --> 00:22:15,530
Why draw such a hard line between us?

394
00:22:15,530 --> 00:22:16,430
Then why haven't you introduced me

395
00:22:16,430 --> 00:22:17,870
to your family?

396
00:22:17,870 --> 00:22:19,640
Are you afraid they won't approve of me as I am now?

397
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,670
You don't know me at all!

398
00:22:21,890 --> 00:22:23,730
Looks like we won't be able to find common ground.
